
# Win11-Golden-Image-Builder v2.5.0

## Highlights

This release introduces a complete Windows 11 image engineering framework focused on offline servicing, security hardening, OEM customization, and deployment-ready ISO creation.

### Features

* Offline AppX removal
* Offline capability removal
* Offline OneDrive removal
* .NET Framework 3.5 enablement
* Default application associations
* OEM customization layer
* Security baseline integration
* LGPO deployment
* AuditMode automation
* ISO creation workflow
* SHA256 validation support

### Security

* Microsoft Security Baseline integration
* CIS-aligned hardening controls
* Credential Guard support
* Hypervisor-Protected Code Integrity support
* Virtualization-Based Security support

### Deployment

Generated images are suitable for:

* Microsoft Intune
* Windows Autopilot
* MECM / SCCM
* MDT
* Hyper-V
* VMware

### Notes

Review all unattend files, certificates, VPN profiles, branding assets, and organizational customizations before distribution outside your environment.
